^-|cs||fp||ht|d|at|^B@2Namyats |CP|1|AT|^*Hwww.larryco.com/bridge-learning-center/detail/214^*N|CP||AT|: Namyats is a convention that employs a 4-of-a-minor opening to show a strong 4-of-a-major opening.|
